headline: 8 Undervalued Stocks for a Rocky Market
summary: Companies that beat average analysts’ forecasts for both profit and revenue over the past two quarters and whose shares recently had price gains in response.

headline: Citigroup (NYSE:C) Q2 Earnings: Leading The Diversified Banks Pack
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Citigroup (NYSE:C) and the best and worst performers in the diversified banks industry.
